# Flutter Conventions

- Comments in English
- File names: snake_case. Classes: PascalCase. Variables: camelCase.
- Always use `const` constructors when possible
- One main widget per file
- Always use `Theme.of(context)` for colors and text styles — never hardcode colors
- Minimum text size: 14px (target audience: 30-50 years old)
- Use named routes for navigation
- Keep widgets small — extract sub-widgets into separate methods or files when > 80 lines
